title: Big Boom AJ, Big Justice, and the Rizzler won an AEW wrestling match. The internet loved it.
description: The Costco guys landed a W in televised PPV wrestling match. The internet loved that it was actually quite well done.
text: Big Boom AJ and his son Big Justice — aka The Costco Guys — won a wrestling match during AEW Full Gear's pre-show on Saturday. Oh, and the Rizzler showed up, too. First of all: what a world. Second: It was actually well-received by people online. AJ, whose real last name is Befumo, defeated QT Marshall in his match with an assist from Big Justice, who, in typical wrestling match fashion, snuck into the ring to deliver a textbook spear to help his dad secure the W. In case you didn't know, AJ was a pro wrestler back in the day so the match was quite well done. Mashable Top Stories The internet loved the Costco guys bringing the boom and the Rizzler, well, doing what it is the Rizzler does. And there were lots of jokes, of course.
